### Installation

```bash
# Recommended (UV - fastest!)
uv tool install git+https://github.com/Data-Wise/aiterm

# Alternative (pipx)
pipx install git+https://github.com/Data-Wise/aiterm
```

**Documentation:** https://data-wise.github.io/aiterm/

